org.apache.commons.functor.generator

Interface Generator<E>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - the type of elements held in this generator.
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseGenerator, CharacterRange, DoubleRange, FilteredGenerator, FloatRange, GenerateUntil, GenerateWhile, IntegerRange, IteratorToGeneratorAdapter, LongRange, LoopGenerator, NumericRange, TransformedGenerator, UntilGenerate, WhileGenerate

    public interface Generator<E>
    The Generator interface defines a number of useful actions applying UnaryFunctors to each in a series of argument Objects.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1376354 $ $Date: 2012-08-23 00:04:55 -0300 (Thu, 23 Aug 2012) $
